{"tid":2079044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藤原拓海車禍身亡，４歲小孩馬路邊玩滑板","createTime":"2020-06-25T13:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T14:18:15.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c483f07f7144674acf53ab24310111bf5409b9","tid":2079044,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nikkansports.com/general/news/202006230001154.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nikkansports.com%2Fgeneral%2Fnews%2F202006230001154.html&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=a1b3a7d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nikkansports.com/general/news/202006230001154.html</a><br />\n<br />\n23日下午1時10分左右，住在東京都世田谷區中町5丁目中町街道上的藤原拓海（4歲男童）被一輛貨車撞擊，送醫後不治。<br />\n<br />\n東京都市警察局多摩川警局逮捕了開車的肇事者 瀨田康彥（47歲，相模原市中央區）。<br />\n<br />\n警方在現場在街上發現一塊破碎的滑板。 就在此之前，有民眾目睹了藤原拓海在滑板上玩耍並用手移動，詳細情況待調查中。"},{"pid":"7f24db01af3aa02d2e1625c9b9fa620993e945e9","tid":2079044,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/67/81/qJean6ablp_YsKSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F67%2F81%2FqJean6ablp_YsKSY.jpg&h=07958f0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88e5ca721e605e0623c2f5542d03c0fae8824071","tid":2079044,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7398ce69cc2f2db5a4a9e1c0b1339d21a19aea","tid":2079044,"uid":253016,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"飄得過就拓海<br />\n飄不過就填海"},{"pid":"17bad3c684625cc83fbb75547cc9891b1eaf681d","tid":2079044,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"たくみくん<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1abfd91ecfe2b4c8f5aba3b9a98ea7249ec2cf","tid":2079044,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"至於車禍的原因，目擊者描述藤原小朋友當時跟奶奶在馬路邊玩滑板，或許是趴在滑板上導致汽車駕駛沒看到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/67/81/qJean6ablp_YsKSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F67%2F81%2FqJean6ablp_YsKSc.jpg&h=1398c0bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來被白色箱型車撞上輾過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/67/81/qJean6ablp_YsKSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F67%2F81%2FqJean6ablp_YsKSa.jpg&h=51bdc7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報案人：「我看到的時候，人已經被捲進車子底下了」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/67/81/qJean6ablp_YsKSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F67%2F81%2FqJean6ablp_YsKSZ.jpg&h=891a88ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67868b0bd0efbd21490aad0bfdf71116812f47de","tid":2079044,"uid":117276,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"你咁樣反架車咪跌左落山咁你咪死囉"},{"pid":"74736d344077abfe7f7905dc2e53625b60a61349","tid":2079044,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c9d4a1491c021ee776b3881eb3467c166529f7","tid":2079044,"uid":337525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a7398ce69cc2f2db5a4a9e1c0b1339d21a19aea","tid":2079044,"uid":253016,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13: